            h1.pull-left=title
    div.container.content-sm
        div.row
            //-Blog posts
            div.col-md-9
                //-Instagram API
                div.news-v3.margin-bottom-30
                    img.img-responsive.full-width(src='/images/blog/instagram-api/instagram-logo-2.jpg', alt='')
                    div.news-v3-in
                        ul.list-inline.posted-info
                            li By&nbsp;
                                a.dark(href='#') Matt Husar
                            li Posted April 27, 2016
                        h2
                            a(href='/blog/posts/instagram-api') Instagram API
                        p.
                            For this post I wanted to work through a basic example of how to request data from an external API and display it on a page. We will be using the Instagram API as our data source, making requests via Javascript, and using a bit of Angular to display the data.
                        p
                            a.btn-u.btn-u-small.btn-brd-hover(href='/blog/posts/instagram-api') <i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Read More
                //-Japan Part 1
                div.news-v3.margin-bottom-30
                    img.img-responsive.full-width(src='/images/gallery/misc/japan_1.jpg', alt='')
                    div.news-v3-in
                        ul.list-inline.posted-info
                            li By&nbsp;
                                a.dark(href='#') Matt Husar
                            li Posted February 20, 2016
                        h2
                            a(href='/blog/posts/japan-part-1') Japan Part 1
                        p.
                            Awhile ago I had the opportunity to spend a few months in Japan.
                            I took a ton of pictures while I was over there, but never had a chance to put a narrative behind them.
                        p Well - I am finally getting around to doing just that. Due to the amount of content I will be breaking this up into multiple parts.
                        p So without further ado this is part 1.
                        p
                            a.btn-u.btn-u-small.btn-brd-hover(href='/blog/posts/japan-part-1') <i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Read More
